                            <head><hi rend="smallcaps">Editor’s Note</hi></head>
                            <p>—In a letter to <persName corresp="#p_BJF1">Byrnes</persName> dated
                                July 20 (<ref target="#d734">document No. 734</ref>, <hi rend="italic">post</hi>) <persName corresp="#p_GAA1">Gromyko</persName> referred to “our conversation this morning”,
                                at which the question of trusteeship was discussed. No minutes of
                                this conversation have been found.</p>
